    \centerline{\includegraphics[width=7.2cm]{Figures/CavityInstalledHall_1.jpg}}
    \caption{The cavity vacuum chamber attached to two ion pumps on the optical table and connected to the electron beam pipe in the Hall A tunnel at JLab. The electron beam pipe above the cavity is used for a straight beam to the experimental Hall when the Compton polarimeter is not used.}
